drupalNodeEvent.title: WildChina LIVE Experience: Chinese New Year Dumpling Making with Mei Zhang

field_description.processed: Dumplings are a culinary staple in Chinese homes for the Lunar New Year. Join WildChina founder’s Mei Zhang (virtually) in her kitchen for a dumpling-making class and a discovery of the dish’s history and traditions. Roll up your sleeves as you learn how to prep, wrap, and cook these mouthwatering treats for you and your family.
